🎯 Project Goal

Create a Python program that:

Generates strong random passwords

Includes:

uppercase

lowercase

numbers

symbols

🧠 Concepts Used

random module

strings

loops

user input

🛠️ Step-by-Step Code
import random
import string

length = int(input("Enter password length: "))

# Character sets
letters = string.ascii_letters
digits = string.digits
symbols = string.punctuation

all_chars = letters + digits + symbols

password = ""

for i in range(length):
    password += random.choice(all_chars)

print("Generated Password:", password)
📌 How It Works

1️⃣ Take password length
2️⃣ Combine all character types
3️⃣ Pick random characters
4️⃣ Generate password

🔥 Example Output
Enter password length: 8
Generated Password: A@3kL!9p
🚀 Upgrade Version (Stronger Password)
password = [
    random.choice(string.ascii_uppercase),
    random.choice(string.ascii_lowercase),
    random.choice(string.digits),
    random.choice(string.punctuation)
]

for i in range(length - 4):
    password.append(random.choice(all_chars))

random.shuffle(password)

print("".join(password))
🧠 Memory Trick

random.choice() → pick random

string → ready-made characters

shuffle() → mix

